model

Class PieceArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.PieceArray

  • public class PieceArray
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a specialized array where each piece has a known location based off of the square it starts on. This allows for constant time add and deletes because the piece also saves it's id (where it is stored in the array). Trading space for time here, but the ArrayList.remove(Piece p) implementation was very expensive since it had to loop over all the pieces for all calls to the remove method.
    Author:
    Matthew
